  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, do not give the genealogy of my fathers in this part of my record;",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.892,
      "end": 8.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither at any time shall I give it",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 8.487,
      "end": 11.134,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after upon these plates which I am writing;",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 11.314,
      "end": 15.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it is given in the record which has been kept by my father;",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 15.72,
      "end": 18.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I do not write it in this work.",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 18.954,
      "end": 22.669,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For it sufficeth me to say that we are descendants of Joseph.",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 23.349,
      "end": 25.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it mattereth not to me",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 25.34,
      "end": 29.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am particular to give a full account of all the things of my father,",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 30.118,
      "end": 32.626,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they cannot be written upon these plates,",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 32.806,
      "end": 34.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I desire the room",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 34.751,
      "end": 37.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may write of the things of God.",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.799,
      "end": 42.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the fulness of mine intent is that I may persuade men to come",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 43.041,
      "end": 44.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the God of Abraham,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 44.986,
      "end": 46.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the God of Isaac,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 46.977,
      "end": 48.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the God of Jacob,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 48.829,
      "end": 50.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be saved.",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 50.809,
      "end": 56.01,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the things which are pleasing unto the world I do not write,",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 56.19,
      "end": 59.069,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but the things which are pleasing unto God",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 59.249,
      "end": 61.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and unto those who are not of the world.",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 62.623,
      "end": 66.57,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I shall give commandment unto my seed,",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 66.75,
      "end": 69.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall not occupy these plates with things",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 69.809,
      "end": 72.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are not of worth unto the children of men.",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    }
  ]
}